n><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> or alternatively,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> they ‘chose’ not to progress. In an interview, one senior manager state</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">d:</span></li></ul><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:6pt 0pt 9pt 90pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">‘</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">As far as it is I'm concerned it's an equal playing field. Women get just the same opportunities as men and are treated just the same - it's up to them - if they're good they'll get on but at the moment there aren't enough good women.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">’</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:6pt 0pt 9pt 46.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">The male scient</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ist continues to manifest the body of the ideal scientist. When women were praised as scientists, it was as operational scientists</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">:</span></li></ul><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:6pt 0pt 9pt 90pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">‘</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">If you give (women) a task they will do it …you say … I think we should do this, or there’s a problem and we’re going to tr</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">y and solve it, try this, try that, and it’s just done, you know they just do it.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">’</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:6pt 0pt 9pt 54pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Though presumably offered as a positive appraisal of women’s potential,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> women who follow instructions and are accommodating are less likely to be seen as having the charact</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">eristics required of a leader in science.</span></p><ol start="18" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold; line-height:150%; margin:6pt 0pt 9pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Issues of fairness dismissed as b</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">usiness </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">or financial </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">problems </span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; line-height:150%; margin:6pt 0pt 9pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">The </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">organiz</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ation</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">VB</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> worked for</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> had developed an equality scheme and a writ